<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1064520>
    dc:description "FIGURE1. Three types of wing-like yolk sac projections.Arrows show a wing-like yolk sac. A, welldeveloped inprolarva of Rhodeus albomarginatus. B, less developed in prolarva of Tanakia lanceolata. C, not developed in prolarva of Acheilognathus omeiensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1064520/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

